<p>
Opening datasource based on ini-file section. 
<p>
The function opens the data source based on external resource definitions passsed in the ini-file. The inifile section name containing the resource definitions is passed as datasource_name to the function. The resource definitions in the data source are filled from the corresponding resource definitions in the ini-file.     </td>
  </tr>
